OL,3,CWhen will the Pink Moon appear and how
OL,4,Cdoes it get its name?
OL,6,FApril's Pink Moon will be visible in
OL,7,Fthe UK for three nights this week,
OL,8,Fstarting Tuesday and reaching its peak
OL,9,Fat 3.12am on Thursday.
OL,11,FHowever, the name Pink Moon, which
OL,12,Fwill be on full display on April 1, is
OL,13,Fsomewhat of an April Fools in itself.
OL,15,FThe night sky event does not mean that
OL,16,Fthe moon will turn pink, or even
OL,17,Fappear to be that colour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
