OL,3,CWhen will the Pink Moon appear and how
OL,4,Cdoes it get its name?
OL,6,FRather, the full moon of April was
OL,7,Fnicknamed by Native Americans after a
OL,8,Fspecies of blooming wildflower called
OL,9,Fthe moss phlox.
OL,11,FEach monthly full moon has an informal
OL,12,Fnickname, often bearing reference to
OL,13,Fseasonal nature events that month,
OL,14,Foriginally designed to help people
OL,15,Fkeep track of the passing seasons.
OL,17,FFor example, June's full moon has been
OL,18,Fdubbed the Strawberry Moon, due to the
OL,19,Fabundance of the fruit in that season.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
