OL,3,CWhen will the Pink Moon appear and how
OL,4,Cdoes it get its name?
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the December full moon has
OL,7,Fbeen nicknamed the Cold Moon because
OL,8,Fof the frosty weather synonymous with
OL,9,Fthat time of year.
OL,11,FSo why is the April Moon significant?
OL,13,FApril's Pink Moon, although not
OL,14,Fnecessarily pink, is still likely to
OL,15,Fbe a colourful lunar spectacle.
OL,17,FThe April Moon can sometimes appear to
OL,18,Fbe an orange, or reddish colour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
