OL,3,CWhen will the Pink Moon appear and how
OL,4,Cdoes it get its name?
OL,6,FThis is due to a phenomenon known as
OL,7,FRayleigh scattering, where reflected
OL,8,Fsunlight passes through a thicker
OL,9,Flayer of Earth's atmosphere, and
OL,10,Fshorter wavelengths like blue and
OL,11,Fviolet are scattered, allowing mainly
OL,12,Fred tones to reach our eyes.
OL,14,FThe full moon in April is also
OL,15,Fconsidered by some to hold specific
OL,16,Fsignificance as it is key for setting
OL,17,Fthe dates for Easter and Passover.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
