OL,3,CWhen will the Pink Moon appear and how
OL,4,Cdoes it get its name?
OL,6,FWednesday night's forecast currently
OL,7,Flooks set to bring clouds and rain
OL,8,Facross England and Wales. Those in
OL,9,FScotland and Northern Ireland will
OL,10,Fhave a better chance of colder air and
OL,11,Fclear spells, making the moon more
OL,12,Fvisible.
OL,14,FThe next full moon, known as the
OL,15,FFlower Moon, will take place on
OL,16,FFriday, May 1.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
